# Deploy to Production

**Never** run `git add`, `git commit`, or `git push` from the project root to deploy.

The `main` branch contains only the built site output. Use the deploy script:

```bash
npm run build
node scripts/deploy-to-main.js
```

This copies `build/` to `deploy-to-main/`, commits only changed files there, and pushes to `origin main`.
